OL,3,CRunner, 26, dies in hospital after
OL,4,Ccollapsing at Great Bristol Run
OL,6,FA runner has died after taking part in
OL,7,Fthe Great Bristol Run.
OL,9,FOrganisers behind the annual event
OL,10,Fsaid a 26-year-old man collapsed
OL,11,Fduring the race on Sunday 19 May.
OL,13,FIn a statement, the Great Run Company
OL,14,Fsaid: "With great sadness, we can
OL,15,Fconfirm the death of a participant at
OL,16,Fthe Great Bristol Run held on Sunday
OL,17,F19 May 2024.
