OL,3,CRunner, 26, dies in hospital after
OL,4,Ccollapsing at Great Bristol Run
OL,6,F"A 26-year-old male collapsed, was
OL,7,Ftreated by medics, and later passed
OL,8,Faway in hospital. The next of kin have
OL,9,Fbeen informed.
OL,11,F"Everyone involved in the organisation
OL,12,Fof the Great Bristol Run would like to
OL,13,Fexpress their sincere condolences to
OL,14,Fthe family and friends of the
OL,15,Fparticipant."
OL,17,FThe cause of the man's death is yet to
OL,18,Fbe determined, ahead of a thorough
OL,19,Fmedical examination.
