OL,6,FThe organisers added: "We take the
OL,7,Fhealth and safety of all participants
OL,8,Fvery seriously and we work hard to
OL,9,Fensure our events are delivered safely.
OL,11,F"All event plans are rigorously
OL,12,Fassessed and signed off by the Bristol
OL,13,FSafety Advisory Group for Events
OL,14,F(SAGE), and align with best practice
OL,15,Fin the UK."
OL,17,FThe event sees runners take on a half-
OL,18,Fmarathon or a 10km run, while there is
OL,19,Falso a race specifically for those who
OL,20,Fare visually impaired, a wheelchair
OL,21,Fevent and a one-mile family race.
